This project is a simple push mode publisher for ESGF data-nodes.
----------------------
Command Line Arguments
----------------------

Example:
Publish
esgpost --schema cmip5 --file_type Dataset --version 1 --publish
Unpublish
esgpost --schema cmip5 --file_type Dataset --version 1 --unpublish --record test_file.xml

--schema, --file_type, --version :
    (required) Specifies mandatory metadata that cannot be harvested directly from netCDF files.

--publish / --unpublish :
    (required) Specifies the type of action the user wishes to accomplish.
    PS: In the case of unpublish --record is used to specify the path of the record describing
    the data to be unpublished.
